00:23:43,061 --> 00:23:45,021
Narrator:
THE EXISTENCE OF SOMA PERIES

440
00:23:45,021 --> 00:23:47,982
MAKES UP ALLELUJAH'S MIND
TO CARRY OUT A CERTAIN MISSION.

441
00:23:47,982 --> 00:23:50,193
IS IT ATONEMENT FOR HIS PAST?

442
00:23:50,193 --> 00:23:52,153
NEXT EPISODE:
"ALLELUJAH".

